{"tid":263234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誤上狼Taxi！ 南非男子慘遭3女輪姦3天","createTime":"2017-05-29T21:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T03:19:07.000Z","uid":41351,"like":32,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4434d3d44328252c51c4861b445c3f1863caa149","tid":263234,"uid":41351,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T21:50:10.000Z","msg":"南非一名男子誤上狼德士，居然被車上三名女子囚禁和輪流性侵長達四天，差點精盡人亡。<br />\n<br />\n根據非洲媒體報導，23歲事主上週五在路邊隨便攔下德士。他看見車上司機外，還載有3名黑妹，不以為意，坐在前座。<br />\n<br />\n忽然，后面妹子忽然在他頸部打了一針，他眼前一黑&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醒來后，小哥發現自己全身衣物不見了，被綁在一張床上。他大驚喊救命，結果房門開了，黑妹走了進來，灌他喝下能量飲料。<br />\n<br />\n於是，他的下半身不由自主的起了反應，然後3名女子輪流玩起了騎馬馬的遊戲！<br />\n<br />\n就這樣，小哥被蹂躪了3天，1天多次。<br />\n<br />\n小哥被榨乾后，終於在周日被丟包到路邊，被路過行人救走送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示男子身心受創，正在全力通緝這3名女色狼。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/30/054858_3872a5e22c261b9342199d762e98f2d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F30%2F054858_3872a5e22c261b9342199d762e98f2d8.jpg&h=2313571d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次真係癡女成真了"},{"pid":"f23b308aa1bf4f930a5075a8e2eebb657c1c3c5d","tid":263234,"uid":37856,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T21:51:57.000Z","msg":"Fake Taxi MEN"},{"pid":"2b70bcdfd71fdcd369122fc1d16e38705fb6590e","tid":263234,"uid":119330,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T22:51:26.000Z","msg":"3個欣宜去野餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6589102a63fa6819cee6663e8d30a436d793d26","tid":263234,"uid":48658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T23:33:04.000Z","msg":"快點..."},{"pid":"801f6a99f6e2c662556fec5fe6cec7d2125915cc","tid":263234,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T23:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3個欣宜去野餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當我冇講過"},{"pid":"0f81a20de0e564e96ac60cb